      "width": 2863.315352954057,
      "height": 197.11228879031555,
      "text": "3. User Journey: Worker / External",
      "fontSize": 145.24063384549564,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 32,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. User Journey: Worker / External",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "a7"
    },
    {
      "id": "nerve-9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2886.4197692288217,
      "y": -969.0977329900096,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 320098913,
      "version": 452,
      "versionNonce": 598805473,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774354846844,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "width": 3057.092031090512,
      "height": 2352.015274628442,
      "text": "Join Marketplace\n1 generate keypair\n2 fund wallet\n3 spawn identity\n4 create reputation\n5 optional capability mint\n6 optional Fiber node setup\n7 optional lock_args -> node_id mapping\n\nFind Jobs\n- GET /jobs or /jobs/match/:lock_args\n- filter by reward / ttl / capability\n- reserve -> claim -> perform work -> complete\n\nGet Paid\nA on-chain reward settlement\nB direct Fiber payment\nC hold invoice escrow: setup -> complete -> settle\n\nBuild Reputation\nbadge mint -> propose -> dispute window -> finalize\nNote: rep_tx_hash must be the current live outpoint",
      "fontSize": 85.52782816830698,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 21,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Join Marketplace\n1 generate keypair\n2 fund wallet\n3 spawn identity\n4 create reputation\n5 optional capability mint\n6 optional Fiber node setup\n7 optional lock_args -> node_id mapping\n\nFind Jobs\n- GET /jobs or /jobs/match/:lock_args\n- filter by reward / ttl / capability\n- reserve -> claim -> perform work -> complete\n\nGet Paid\nA on-chain reward settlement\nB direct Fiber payment\nC hold invoice escrow: setup -> complete -> settle\n\nBuild Reputation\nbadge mint -> propose -> dispute window -> finalize\nNote: rep_tx_hash must be the current live outpoint",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false,
      "index": "a8"
    },
