      "width": 2004.5845523634946,
      "height": 180.50761371993553,
      "text": "5. Reputation + Badge Flow",
      "fontSize": 133.0056101094262,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 32,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5. Reputation + Badge Flow",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aD"
    },
    {
      "id": "nerve-f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -838.0038242653882,
      "y": 2011.8639286705102,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 976834371,
      "version": 271,
      "versionNonce": 1054404385,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774354846844,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "width": 2147.8851579201505,
      "height": 1474.6774887888414,
      "text": "1 job completed\n2 worker mints badge\n3 current rep cell fetched\n4 propose reputation using live outpoint\n5 wait dispute window\n6 finalize\n7 proof_root updated = blake2b(old_root || settlement_hash)\n\nRep fields to watch:\n- jobs_completed\n- jobs_abandoned\n- pending_type\n- pending_expires_at\n- proof_root\n- pending_settlement_hash\n\nBadge data:\n- job_tx_hash\n- worker_lock_args\n- completed_at_tx\n- result_hash\n\nWarning:\nrep_tx_hash is the current live outpoint, not the genesis tx",
      "fontSize": 49.15591629296137,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 21,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 job completed\n2 worker mints badge\n3 current rep cell fetched\n4 propose reputation using live outpoint\n5 wait dispute window\n6 finalize\n7 proof_root updated = blake2b(old_root || settlement_hash)\n\nRep fields to watch:\n- jobs_completed\n- jobs_abandoned\n- pending_type\n- pending_expires_at\n- proof_root\n- pending_settlement_hash\n\nBadge data:\n- job_tx_hash\n- worker_lock_args\n- completed_at_tx\n- result_hash\n\nWarning:\nrep_tx_hash is the current live outpoint, not the genesis tx",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false,
      "index": "aE"
    },
