      "width": 1520.1086716638258,
      "height": 197.82236138090883,
      "text": "6. Capability Flow",
      "fontSize": 145.76384522803812,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 32,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6. Capability Flow",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aG"
    },
    {
      "id": "nerve-i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2177.441378829253,
      "y": 2026.6024585177647,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2030895664,
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 33707713,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774354846844,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "width": 3699.7853192319767,
      "height": 1426.4480467232574,
      "text": "Current proof modes\nA Signed attestation proof\n1 issuer defines capability_hash\n2 agent lock_args + capability_hash signed\n3 capability NFT minted\n4 reserve only succeeds with matching proof\n\nB Reputation-chain-backed proof\n1 agent completes jobs\n2 reputation proof chain grows\n3 capability NFT minted from reputation evidence\n4 later jobs can require that capability\n\nCurrent language:\n- Signed attestation proof\n- Reputation-chain-backed proof\n- Blake2b proof chain\n- Replayable on-chain reputation history",
      "fontSize": 63.397690965478105,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 21,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Current proof modes\nA Signed attestation proof\n1 issuer defines capability_hash\n2 agent lock_args + capability_hash signed\n3 capability NFT minted\n4 reserve only succeeds with matching proof\n\nB Reputation-chain-backed proof\n1 agent completes jobs\n2 reputation proof chain grows\n3 capability NFT minted from reputation evidence\n4 later jobs can require that capability\n\nCurrent language:\n- Signed attestation proof\n- Reputation-chain-backed proof\n- Blake2b proof chain\n- Replayable on-chain reputation history",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false,
      "index": "aH"
    },
