      "width": 2312.1810467310615,
      "height": 798.7836397606223,
      "text": "[VERIFIED][ON-CHAIN]\n1 parent agent exists on-chain\n2 parent identity cell is live\n3 spawn_sub_agent called\n4 builder now:\n- uses actual parent_lock_args\n- includes parent identity as cell dep\n- parent lock input present\n- parent identity dep ordered before secp dep group\n5 child identity cell created\n6 child gets pubkey, lock_args, spending limit, daily limit, parent_lock_args, revenue_share_bps\n7 optional initial funding cell\n",
