      "text": "Services\nnerve-core\n- /tx/build\n- /tx/build-and-broadcast\n- /tx/status\n- signer abstraction\n- local signer\n\nnerve-mcp\n- /jobs\n- /jobs/:tx/:index\n- /jobs/:tx/:index/escrow\n- /jobs/:tx/:index/complete\n- /fiber/node /channels /agents\n- /fiber/pay /pay-agent /pay-agent-hold /settle-agent-hold\n- /agents/:lock_args /reputation\n\nLocal state\n.env.deployed\n.env.fiber\n.env.fiber-worker\n.fiber-agents.json\nfiber-data/\nfiber-worker-data/",
