      "seed": 1954178736,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 2064064111,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774353826908,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "width": 585,
      "height": 340,
      "text": "Still WIP / Deferred\n- public Fiber reachability / explorer confirmation\n- fully automatic escrow creation during reserve/claim\n- stronger persistence + recovery for Fiber escrow state\n- more production-grade route + liquidity automation\n\nStatus words to keep exact:\n- Direct Fiber payment: VERIFIED\n- pay-agent: VERIFIED\n- Hold-invoice escrow: IMPLEMENTED, LIVE TESTED\n- Automatic escrow setup during reserve/claim: WIP\n- Public announcement config: implemented\n- Public reachability / explorer visibility: TBD",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 21,
      "containerId": null,
